snippet.title: Soccer Story - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer
snippet.description: Join a member of the team at No More Robots for a look at what you can expect from Soccer Story, including a peek at some of the sports, activities, rivals you'll encounter, and more available in the upcoming open-world RPG.
